# Stage 1 test: 2D rectangular specimen using #@rect.
# Coordinates are 2D (`coords 2 x y`); the generator writes a 2-line
# header to nodes.dat so qvoronoi sees a 2D point set.
#@output nodes.dat
#@domain 2
#@diam 0.008
#@maxiter 100000
#@perflag 2 0 0
#@ranint -1
#@ranflag 1
# bounding-box corners widen the localiser
#@vertex 1 coords 2 -0.01 -0.01 refine 1. radius 0.
#@vertex 2 coords 2  0.11  0.06 refine 1. radius 0.
#@controlvertex 1 coords 2 0.0  0.025
#@controlvertex 2 coords 2 0.10 0.025
#@rect 1 box 4 0. 0. 0.10 0.05 refine 1.
